Well. you know.
you can't really blame her.

1284
01:13:18.316 --> 01:13:21.236
I know. I just...

1285
01:13:22.152 --> 01:13:24.947
Hey. you were honest.

1286
01:13:25.572 --> 01:13:29.827
It's okay to not be okay
if you're not okay.

1287
01:13:29.952 --> 01:13:30.661
Look. I...

1288
